    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Tendrils creep from your sprouts, draining vital essence from the inflicted. Make an attack. If it hits, it deals an additional [[/roll 5d6]] damage. You may heal yourself and allies within Close range of the struck creature for a number of hit points equal to [[/roll 5d6]] + three times your initiation modifier, divided as you choose between you and other creatures. If the target is sprouted, this maneuver heals an additional d6 per sprout stack the target has, to a maximum of 9d6.</p>"
